Introduction

Koo Jungmo, also known by the mononym Jungmo is a vocalist under Starship Entertainment. He is a member of the boy band CRAVITY. He was a contestant in Produce X 101 where he finished at 12th place.

He debuted as a member of CRAVITY on April 14, 2020 with the mini album "HIDEOUT : REMEMBER WHO WE ARE".
